createUser

This web service allows to create a new user. The user will receive an email with a link to validate his account The links has a TTL of 72h. If the token expires, updating the user (even without any changements) will send a new email. Security access The connected user can manage the customer (he belongs to the customer or he is SUPER_ADMIN) Rules If the customer has a limited number of users, then this limit cannot be exceeded.
